:

1. *Bili* smo na odmoru skoro celu nedelju. (We were on vacation for almost a full week.)
2. *Bili* su zabrinuti zbog svoje bezbednosti. (They were worried about their safety.)
3. Moraćemo da budemo *bili* da bi dobili dobre ocene. (We will have to be diligent to get good grades.)
4. *Bila* je to lepa prilika da se družimo. (It was a nice opportunity to socialize.)
5. Oni su *bili* neverovatno dobri prema nama. (They were unbelievably kind to us.)